headline: Morgan Stanley Lifts Equinix (EQIX) Price Target to $1,075 on Accelerating Revenue and AFFO Growth
summary: We recently published an article titled 12 Best Data Storage Stocks to Buy Right Now. On February 13, Morgan Stanley raised its price target on Equinix, Inc. (NASDAQ:EQIX) to $1,075 from $950 and reiterated an Overweight rating after the company increased its 2026 revenue and adjusted funds from operations (AFFO) growth guidance. The analyst cited […]
